      "text": "\n\nimport sys\n\ndef main():\n    x, k, d = map(int, sys.stdin.readline().rstrip().split())\n    if abs(x) < k * d:\n        print(abs(x - (x // d) * d))\n    else:\n        print(abs(x) - (k * d))\n\nif __name__ == '__main__':\n    main()"
